                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>March 25\n                5622/1862</date>.</p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir &amp; <hi rend=\"underline\">Colleague</hi>!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">The above address<lb/> will no doubt excite your curiosity &amp;\n                astonishment<lb/> I will at once gratify both. After 4 months'<lb/> reflection &amp;\n                upon the most urgent solicitations of<lb/> my friends &amp; the congregation itself,\n                I have accepted<lb/> the <hi rend=\"underline\">unanimous</hi> election, or rather <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">invitation</hi> (for<lb/> I did not apply for the place) as\n                Minister<lb/> of the congregation <hi rend=\"underline\">Anche-Emeth</hi> at\n                    <placeName>Albany</placeName>,<lb/> formerly <persName>Dr Wise's</persName>\n                congregation. What do you<lb/> say to this, that <persName>Dr. W.</persName> must\n                see me at the<lb/> head of his former flock?</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As I intend <add>אי\"ה</add> to<lb/> enter upon my duties a fortnight\n                hence, and<lb/> shall, in consequence, be more than occupied<lb/> with winding up my\n                business here and<lb/> preparing for my removal, it will be im-<lb/>possible for me\n                to continue, for the next 2<lb/> months, my translation for the <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Occident</hi>; but<lb/> rely upon it, as soon as I shall be comfortably<lb/>\n                settled, I shall recommence, &amp; finish the work<lb/> without interruption.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3736mn6b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
